# AMQP Support for Mantis

*  https://github.com/...

---

## Supporting services

* GitHub

## Install

### Getting code

Download zip or git clone on your server.

Copy MantisAmq folder in plugins folder
Make sure folder name is "MantisAmq"
Go to Manage interface and install the plugin.

## Config
Clic on "MantisAmq 0.1" and configure your AMQP Server

Exemple for Canopsis :
Activate Amqp report: 	Yes
AMQP Server IP: 	192.168.0.1
Port: 	5672
User: 	guest
Password: guest	
Vhost: 	canopsis
Exchange:  canopsis.events	
	


